[[Nachi Falls]] is considered a Kannabi<ref name="nachi2">{{cite web |last=Kamizaka |first=Jirō |title=Hiryū Gongen |url=http://www.kkr.mlit.go.jp/wakayama/rekishi/disco131.html |access-date=28 March 2010 |publisher=Ministry of Land, Infrastructure and Transport - Kinki Regional Development Bureau |language=ja}}</ref>, as is [[Mount Miwa]].<ref name="Tamura20" />
