Shrines dedicated to ''kannabi'' often lack a [[honden|''honden'']] or [[Haiden (Shinto)|''haiden'']], and instead enshrine the natural ''kannabi'' as deities. [[Ōmiwa Shrine]] is one such example.<ref name=":2" />
